{
  "meta": {
    "week": "W02",
    "lesson": "02",
    "scene": "convenience.store",
    "title_zh": "結帳：袋子、發票、找零"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi! Are you ready to check out?",
      "zh": "你好！準備結帳了嗎？",
      "ja": "こんにちは！お会計の準備はできましたか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I am.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you need a bag?",
      "zh": "需要袋子嗎？",
      "ja": "袋は必要ですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, a small bag, please.",
      "zh": "要，一個小袋子，謝謝。",
      "ja": "はい、小さい袋をお願いします。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That’s two dollars.",
      "zh": "那是兩元。",
      "ja": "2ドルです。"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want a receipt?",
      "zh": "需要收據嗎？",
      "ja": "レシートは必要ですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, please.",
      "zh": "好的，謝謝。",
      "ja": "はい、お願いします。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you have a membership app?",
      "zh": "你有會員 App 嗎？",
      "ja": "会員アプリはお持ちですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I don’t.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ、持っていません。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No worries. Cash or card?",
      "zh": "沒關係。付現還是刷卡？",
      "ja": "大丈夫です。現金とカード、どちらですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cash.",
      "zh": "付現。",
      "ja": "現金で。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your total is eighty-five.",
      "zh": "總共是八十五。",
      "ja": "合計は85です。"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "どうぞ。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Out of one hundred?",
      "zh": "收你一百嗎？",
      "ja": "100からでよろしいですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here’s your change: fifteen.",
      "zh": "找你十五。",
      "ja": "お釣りは15です。"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Would you like the receipt in the bag?",
      "zh": "收據要放進袋子裡嗎？",
      "ja": "レシートは袋に入れますか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, in the bag is fine.",
      "zh": "好，放袋子裡就好。",
      "ja": "はい、袋に入れてください。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Any ice for your drink?",
      "zh": "飲料需要加冰嗎？",
      "ja": "飲み物に氷は必要ですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, thanks.",
      "zh": "不用，謝謝。",
      "ja": "いいえ、結構です。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want a straw?",
      "zh": "你要吸管嗎？",
      "ja": "ストローは必要ですか？"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, please.",
      "zh": "好的，謝謝。",
      "ja": "はい、お願いします。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All set. Have a nice day.",
      "zh": "都好了。祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "これで完了です。よい一日を。"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You too.",
      "zh": "你也是。",
      "ja": "あなたも。"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Next customer, please.",
      "zh": "下一位客人，請。",
      "ja": "次のお客様どうぞ。"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "(Waits)",
      "zh": "（等待）",
      "ja": "（待つ）"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thanks for coming in!",
      "zh": "謝謝光臨！",
      "ja": "ご来店ありがとうございます！"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you!",
      "zh": "謝謝你！",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます！"
    }
  ]
}
